{"tid":2442312,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵去年香港客運業務虧損擴大逾8倍","createTime":"2021-03-11T09:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T07:28:44.000Z","uid":70964,"like":92,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"addcce95ff808cf89368461e352e11a41e6b50c0","tid":2442312,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"港鐵去年業績轉虧48.09億元，受到投資物業重估轉虧91.9億元，及經常性業務表現不理想拖累。期內，香港客運業務虧損擴大逾8倍至54.08億元，香港車站商務盈利貢獻減少51%至25.02億元，中國內地及國際鐵路、物業租賃及管理業務盈利貢獻急跌76%至2.61億元。不過，香港物業發展錄得54.42億元利潤，主要來自「日出康城」第六期所錄得的分佔盈餘及出售存貨單位，抵銷部分對業績不利的影響。港鐵去年本地鐵路服務總乘客11.45億人次，按年減少27%；輕鐵及巴士總乘客1.54億人次，跌近26%。<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-11 17:17:54 (1)"},{"pid":"96b159b9700f5981c4473edd00e77b4f20e98932","tid":2442312,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"99c231af1080fb289dcbfdf7a2913329087ad312","tid":2442312,"uid":2054,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:28:27.000Z","msg":"兩單惡襲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQTNsD0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQTNsD0.png&h=ac0d94b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58449feb68db0803e36d570ce9f99ab75af2effc","tid":2442312,"uid":149844,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"轉搭巴士好耐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d656beb8340db87748aca3b324cbd43fd9fefd0","tid":2442312,"uid":70964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黨鐵"},{"pid":"e32befa38b1d25bbe9eaed5286856969c95a4e91","tid":2442312,"uid":115579,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"罷買黨鐵商鋪，罷唔到都買少d啦<br />\n反抗冇槍，議會俾人dq,  罷工又話有